<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vansang pi khin vanmi nih, Leicung ah hla an run sak, Tlang nih a hun
 lehnak ah, An hla kha an rak hrawlter.

[C1]
   (Glori-a in excelsis De-o, Glori-a in excelsis De-o) Pathian cu cung
   nung bik ah thang'hat, Pathian cu, cung nung bik ah thang'hat.

[V2]
 Bethlehem khua ah ra law, Ngakchia cu ra zoh tuah u, Khukbil in bia
 cio tuah u, Bawipa Khrih kan Siangpahrang.

[C2]
   (Glori-a in excelsis De-o, Glori-a in excelsis De-o) Pathian cu cung
   nung bik ah thang'hat, Pathian cu, cung nung bik ah thang'hat.

[V3]
 Vanmi nih an thangthatmi, Cu cawkuang ah nan hmuh lai, Mary le Josef
 le tiah, Bawi Khrih thangthat cio u si.

[C3]
   (Glori-a in excelsis De-o, Glori-a in excelsis De-o) Pathian cu cung
   nung bik ah thang'hat, Pathian cu, cung nung bik ah thang'hat.</lyrics>
<title>VANMI HLA AN SA CH91</title>
</song>